- There is sufficient padding and spacing to ensure that the UI remains accessible and user-friendly. 
- All elements are responsive within a safe margin of 24px from the edge of the viewport, with minimum spacing of 16px between interactive elements.

### Conclusion:
This interactive module for understanding weighted graphs provides an engaging hands-on experience. By manipulating the number of nodes and seeing their relationships dynamically visualized, learners can better grasp the concept of weighted graphs and their significance in various applications.

