- The reset button will be positioned centrally, beneath the graph, with clear spacing (16 px) from other elements.
- The implementation will ensure accessibility through semantic HTML and screen-reader-friendly labels.

### Example HTML, CSS, and JavaScript Code

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
