Here's a complete interactive HTML module designed to provide users with an in-depth understanding of the Selection Sort algorithm. The module is organized to ensure clarity and interactivity, using only vanilla HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

### Complete Interactive HTML Page Code:

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Interactive Selection Sort</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 24px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
