   - Input field and button are also flexbox-aligned, maintaining a consistent and clear organization.
   - Visual cues (highlighting of array elements) as feedback during the search process enhance the users' understanding while interacting with the module. 

### Accessibility and Responsiveness:
- The module uses basic font and background colors for contrast.
- All interactive elements are clearly labeled and accessible via keyboard navigation.
- Responsive design principles have been applied, ensuring that the layout remains functional and visually appealing on different devices.

This interactive design effectively helps users learn about Linear Search through hands-on experience. The minimalist approach ensures clarity while maintaining user engagement.

