- The visual feedback includes updating the result matrix cells, and a simplified animation with class changes for updated and unchanged cells.
- The reset functionality clears the matrix for new inputs, maintaining interactivity within the learning experience. 

This straightforward approach and layout ensure clarity, focus on the subject matter, and an engaging pedagogical experience for learners.

