The above HTML document provides a simple yet functional interactive module for learning about Topological Sort. By allowing users to create nodes and edges while visually representing the sorting process, the module fosters a deeper understanding of directed graphs and their sorting algorithms. The use of animations, visual feedback, and clear layout contributes to an engaging learning experience.

