- **Spacing** of **16px** will be maintained between interactive elements.
- Responsive design will be applied to ensure that the module looks good on various screen sizes.

### Complete HTML Structure

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
