- **Visual Feedback:**
  - When the user clicks the button, a series of boxes will animate onto the screen representing stacked recursive calls.
  - Each box will display the current value of the recursive call.
  - As the function "unwinds" (i.e., once the base case is reached and the function returns), these boxes will fade out sequentially while updating the total result in a final display.

